# Sitemapy
[![PyPI - Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/sitemapy)](https://pypi.org/project/sitemapy/)
[![Python Support](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/sitemapy.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/sitemapy/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

**Sitemapy** is a Python package for generating SEO-friendly XML sitemaps.

## Features

- üöÄ Simple and intuitive API for sitemap generation
- üìù Support for all standard sitemap attributes (priority, changefreq, lastmod)
- üåç Full hreflang support for multilingual sites
- üì¶ Sitemap index support for large sites
- üóúÔ∏è Built-in compression (gzip) support
- üîí Safe XML parsing with defusedxml
- ‚ö° Method chaining for cleaner code
- üîÑ Load and modify existing sitemaps

